                                    </div>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <div class="thum-img">
                                        <div class="ratio"><img src="../../img/img_prd.jpg" alt="sampleImg" class="vertical"></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="radio">
                                        <input type="radio" id="r-vote13" name="r-vote1">
                                        <label for="r-vote13">시원한 바다가 생각나는 <br>파란색</label>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <div class="thum-img">
                                        <div class="ratio"><img src="../../img/img_prd.jpg" alt="sampleImg" class="vertical"></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="radio">
                                        <input type="radio" id="r-vote14" name="r-vote1">
                                        <label for="r-vote14">새콤, 탱글탱글 감귤이 떠오르는<br>주황색</label>
                                    </div>
